Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:36.80,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}如同燃燒的火焰般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:39.32,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}能在此找到自己的容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:42.71,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}雷達之下尋找自己的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:49.17,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}舉起鋼刃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:57.74,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}縱情呻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:03:04.95,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}繼續這不羈的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.21,0:22:17.53,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}燃焦這唯一的身體
